     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 9 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20less|20than|2018|20months-42\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageislessthan18months-42\">Client's age is less than 18 months-42</a></td><td>Client's age is less than 18 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" &lt; 18 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20not|20due|20for|20Hepatitis|20A|20vaccination-48\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-ClientisnotdueforHepatitisAvaccination-48\">Client is not due for Hepatitis A vaccination-48</a></td><td>Client is not due for Hepatitis A vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20hepatitis|20A|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-131\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-NohepatitisAprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-131\">No hepatitis A primary series dose was administered-131</a></td><td>No hepatitis A primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Hepatitis A-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20more|20than|20or|20equal|20to|2018|20months-42\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageismorethanorequalto18months-42\">Client's age is more than or equal to 18 months-42</a></td><td>Client's age is more than or equal to 18 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" ≥ 18 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Livevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nolivevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) ≥ 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20Hepatitis|20A|20vaccination-44\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-ClientisdueforHepatitisAvaccination-44\">Client is due for Hepatitis A vaccination-44</a></td><td>Client is due for Hepatitis A vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-One|20hepatitis|20A|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-131\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-OnehepatitisAprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-131\">One hepatitis A primary series dose was administered-131</a></td><td>One hepatitis A primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Hepatitis A-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTHepatitisALiveAttenuatedHAV1DoseVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Hepatitis|20A|20immunization|20schedule|20is|20complete-158\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-HepatitisAimmunizationscheduleiscomplete-158\">Hepatitis A immunization schedule is complete-158</a></td><td>Hepatitis A immunization schedule is complete</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Complete\"\n\"Completed the primary vaccination series\" = TRUE (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Hepatitis A-containing vaccines\")</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
